data.description: Step into immaculate living in this stunning home boasting an open concept design with 10ft ceilings! The family room is oversized and has a fireplace! The kitchen is the heart of the home with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large walk-in pantry with beverage fridge! Stepping up a few steps are 3 bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms providing the perfect amount of comfort and privacy. The basement is fully finished and great for large family gatherings! Outside, indulge in picturesque views no matter where you are. The front and back porches are large and covered and make for the perfect place to relax with a good book or a cup of coffee! Backyard is fully fenced in and has a shed for additional storage! Schedule your showing today! Agent related to seller.
